Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:21.38,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,想利用我的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:21.92,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:23.56,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,别看  别翻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:25.72,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,这个痕迹是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:27.12,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,樱小姐的大招
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.28,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,Sakurament Cannon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:30.28,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,出现了让人心跳不已的单词
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:32.98,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,樱小姐的大招  Sakurament Cannon是怎么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:34.90,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我在整理思绪稍后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:37.04,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,之后会说明吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:38.20,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,会的会的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.48,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,完全没有诚意的回应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:43.82,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,Sakurament Cannon是开放的樱花一样的棱镜在飞舞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:47.60,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,然后景色突然变成粉红色  轰出巨大光束那样的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:48.74,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:50.74,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,顺便一提Fresh Peach Heart Shower是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:52.32,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,你们两个吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:54.08,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,蜜柑！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:57.84,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,这个工厂被姐姐破坏了两次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:00.52,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,第一次是帮助蜜柑的时候
