Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.17,0:12:04.93,mazoku - hon,,0,0,0,,{\pos(302.857,659.428)}工厂被破坏（第一次）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.17,0:12:04.93,mazoku - hon,,0,0,0,,{\pos(304,720)}仓库没事（蜜柑证实）
